CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 18, 1961, pg. 19 reads: Swing Your Partner - Loendi Club took on the air of an old-fashioned barn recently when the Loendi Ladies Auxlliary [sic] sponsored a square dance in club's parlors. It was "swing your partner and circle to the left," as the group in the first photo demonstrates...-Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of men, and women, including one on far right wearing striped sweater and dark trousers, square dancing in Loendi Club, sponsored by the Loendi Ladies Auxiliary
